## OUTPUT REQUIREMENTS:
- Photorealistic, editorial quality
- Natural lighting, authentic feel
- No AI-looking artifacts
- Clean composition with clear focal point
- Ultra high resolution output
- No text, watermark, logos, blurry, low resolution, warped features, extra limbs

## ABSOLUTELY DO NOT:
- Generate ANY text, letters, words, logos, watermarks, or branding elements
- Generate ANY logo or brand mark — a real logo will be added separately
- Use cluttered or busy compositions
- Create images that look obviously AI-generated or synthetic
- Ignore the brand color palette
- Create abstract or unrelated imagery that does not connect to the business

PROHIBITED: text, watermark, logos, blurry, low resolution, warped features, extra limbs
